  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate a single breath hold abdominal MRI protocol and
      compare the image quality of respiratory triggered 3D T1-weighted images against conventional
      breath hold images.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
